leve.name: Sylph Strands
leve.description: Sylphs under the thrall of the primal Ramuh are raising a new fort, using brute strength to squeeze out sylphs friendly to us. Neither the intimidation nor the structure must be allowed to stand. Your prowess as a slayer of sylphs precedes you. We petition you to go in our stead and do this bloody yet righteous deed.
leve.client: The Order of the Twin Adder Red Otters
